OL,3,CRain falls in Iran's capital for first
OL,4,Ctime in months amid record drought
OL,6,FIran is facing a major water shortage
OL,7,Ffollowing years of drought conditions.
OL,8,FWater is being restricted in the
OL,9,Fcapital Tehran and evacuations could
OL,10,Fbe a possibility. David Harper on why
OL,11,FTehran is about to run out of water
OL,13,FRain has fallen for the first time in
OL,14,Fmonths in Iran's capital, as the
OL,15,Fcountry endures the driest autumn in
OL,16,Fmore than half a century.
