OL,3,CRain falls in Iran's capital for first
OL,4,Ctime in months amid record drought
OL,6,FThe dry conditions have become so
OL,7,Fsevere, the president warned that the
OL,8,Fgovernment may have to leave Tehran by
OL,9,Fthe end of December if there is no
OL,10,Fsignificant rainfall to refill dams
OL,11,Faround the city.
OL,13,FGovernment-sponsored billboards call
OL,14,Fon the public not to use garden hoses
OL,15,Foutside to avoid waste.
OL,17,FWater supplies have reportedly been
OL,18,Fcut out for hours at a time in some
OL,19,Fparts of Tehran, a city home to ten
OL,20,Fmillion people.
