OL,3,CRain falls in Iran's capital for first
OL,4,Ctime in months amid record drought
OL,6,FLevels of snow on the nearby Alborz
OL,7,FMountains have remained low, with
OL,8,Fsatellite pictures showing reservoirs
OL,9,Frunning noticeably low - including the
OL,10,FLatyan Dam, which is currently under
OL,11,F10% full.
OL,13,FMeteorologists have described this
OL,14,Fautumn as the driest in more than 50
OL,15,Fyears across the country, from even
OL,16,Fbefore its 1979 Islamic Revolution.
