OL,3,CRain falls in Iran's capital for first
OL,4,Ctime in months amid record drought
OL,6,FThe country's newspaper has said:
OL,7,F"Iran is facing an unprecedented water
OL,8,Fcrisis that threatens not only its
OL,9,Fagricultural sector but also regional
OL,10,Fstability and global food markets."
OL,12,FAgriculture uses an estimated 90% of
OL,13,Fthe country's water supplies.
